---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Trevize.ai - Guiding Humanity in the Age of Superintelligence">
	<main>
		<section class="hero section">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>Where is <span class="gradient-text">Golan Trevize</span>?</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">Guiding Humanity in the Age of Superintelligence</p>
				<div class="hero-content">
					<p>
						In Isaac Asimov's <em>Foundation</em> series, the character Golan Trevize stands apart as the human whose intuition shapes the fate of the galaxy. Even in a universe ruled by the grand predictive science of psychohistory and guided by immensely powerful AI, Trevize's final judgment remains indispensable—because it arises from a place no algorithm can replicate.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mission section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Our <span class="gradient-text">Mission</span></h2>
				<p>
					At <strong>trevize.ai</strong>, we believe in preserving and amplifying that spark of human insight. In a future where advanced artificial general intelligence (AGI) and even artificial superintelligence (ASI) reshape how we live and work, <em>our</em> mission is to ensure humanity's unique perspective remains vital.
				</p>
				<p>
					We stand at the intersection of technological innovation and timeless human wisdom, translating the intangible qualities of creativity, ethics, and intuition into real-world impact.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="approach section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>The Trevize <span class="gradient-text">Approach</span></h2>
				<div class="grid">
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Intuition That Goes Beyond Logic</h3>
						<p>Like Golan Trevize, sometimes the path to the best decision isn't purely rational. At critical junctures, human insight can tip the balance. We help organizations balance the precision of data with the power of intuition.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Complement to Advanced AI</h3>
						<p>Artificial superintelligence promises remarkable progress, but it can overlook the subtle, human dimensions of problems. Our work is dedicated to forging a symbiotic relationship between human creativity and machine intelligence.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Future-Focused Ethics</h3>
						<p>In Asimov's universe, robots and predictive tools can guide humanity. Yet they must turn to humans when faced with dilemmas no statistical model can solve. We champion ethical frameworks that preserve humanity's agency.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Shaping Galactic-Scale Possibilities</h3>
						<p>Trevize's biggest decision involved the future of an entire galaxy. Today's AI breakthroughs hold equally transformative potential for our global society. We believe your mission demands the same high-level vision.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="future section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Where We're <span class="gradient-text">Heading</span></h2>
				<p>
					The Trevize organization is built on the premise that maintaining human relevance requires both technological prowess and deep human understanding. Our team spans disciplines—from machine learning experts to philosophers—united by a commitment to steering the future of AI for collective benefit.
				</p>
				<p>
					By nurturing human insight alongside technological innovation, we strive to enable meaningful progress in every field that matters.
				</p>
				<p class="closing-quote">
					<em>"Because the final say should remain human."</em>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
			rgba(var(--background), 0.8) 0%,
			rgba(var(--background), 1) 100%
		);
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		font-weight: 300;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hero-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}

	.card {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.1);
		border-radius: 8px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.closing-quote {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>